          '    * php.wasm.RAND_bytes\n' +
          '    * php.wasm.zif_openssl_random_pseudo_bytes\n' +
          '    * php.wasm.ZEND_DO_ICALL_SPEC_RETVAL_USED_HANDLER\n' +
          '    * php.wasm.execute_ex\n'
      }
    }
  }
}
